entries.femaleVariant: Forty-five, forty-six... Fuck, we're still short.
Fuuuuuck... I could kill for a pack o' Morleys. You said your mom had you covered for smokes...
I mean, she does, but... well, you know...
Ever since she stopped working she's been having these attacks of, like, extreme fatigue. Sometimes she sleeps two days straight.
Choom, if my mom slept for two days straight? I'd call Trauma, stat.
Yeah, with what eddies? You wouldn't lift a fuckin' pinky finger and you know it.
Anyway, lately she started forgetting all kinds o' shit...
So go ask her for more eds! Maybe she'll forget she already gave you some.
